title: New Team Rider Nick Tucker
description:
Nick was invited as a guest on the Three Amigos tour last year and he's been impressing the team ever since. So much so that he earned himself a spot on the SUPRA roster.

"It's truly an honor to be a part of SUPRA and grow with the whole team and the brand," Nick said. "I couldn't be more proud to lace up a pair of SUPRAs every morning. And it's a great feeling knowing I'm repping the best shoes in the game." 

The newest SUPRA team rider is wearing the newest SUPRA team shoe for this switch f/s feeble: the black suede and black canvas Pistol low top. 

SUPRA looks forward to a long and productive relationship with Nick Tucker. The Pistol low top is available at better skate retailers and suprafootwear.com.
